              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best overall · Content + local + social</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$99<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Content SEO module</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>30 articles/month written, optimized, and auto-published</li>
                <li>Google Business Profile add-on ($49/mo) — SEO.AI has none</li>
                <li>Social media posts add-on ($49/mo)</li>
                <li>WordPress, Webflow, Ghost, custom webhook integrations</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Fewer CMS integrations than SEO.AI (no Wix, Squarespace)</li>
                <li>No brand-voice training UI</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Local service businesses and SMBs who want content + local + social in one subscription.</div>
            <a href="/checkout/" class="tool-cta-btn">Start $1 trial →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">02</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Scalenut</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best budget automation · GEO features</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$30<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Starter annual</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>80% cheaper than SEO.AI on annual billing</li>
