              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Content is formulaic and often sounds robotic</li>
                <li>Cancellation complaints across review sites</li>
                <li>WordPress-only publishing</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Budget teams who want automation + GEO at a fraction of SEO.AI's price.</div>
            <a href="/alternatives/scalenut/" class="tool-cta-btn">Read alternatives →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">03</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Surfer SEO</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best content optimization editor</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$99<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Essential annual</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
